{"tid":2425511,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"湯怡麥秋成 係咪拎免費PR品做生意？","createTime":"2021-02-27T11:27:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T17:41:01.000Z","uid":223376,"like":115,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"16c8e40f53ce1129a97f8077af4a96a165dfb0cb","tid":2425511,"uid":223376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T11:27:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CLCIMiKgXh3/?igshid=hjdceclieg2z\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCLCIMiKgXh3%2F%3Figshid%3Dhjdceclieg2z&d=vb5EudyRk00tD8HubIiEm6ooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=cba6df6e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCLCIMiKgXh3%2F%3Figshid%3Dhjdceclieg2z&h=b6bba21f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CLCIMiKgXh3/?igshid=hjdceclieg2z</a><br />\n本身見佢哋結婚就八卦入麥秋成嘅IG睇吓，見到佢自己原來有個&rdquo;成老師醒目折扣屋&rdquo;嘅網，入到去個網橫睇掂睇都似係每樣剩係得一件嘅PR品多過批發嘅商品。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/52feLz6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F52feLz6.png&h=2436c976&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n入邊每樣貨品都係得一件，完全唔似係攞一批貨返嚟賣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ShVm911.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FShVm911.png&h=8b7451e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n連呢款已經賣出嘅鞋都係得一對一個size，38號<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fbQygHf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfbQygHf.png&h=50d77a73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n所以對於佢網站聲稱竭力幫人搵低於市價嘅產品好有保留<br />\n<br />\n網入邊全部清一色女性化妝護膚品，或者手袋高踭鞋，好難唔令人聯想其實全部產品都係湯怡或者男方自己平時收收買埋嘅PR禮物<br />\n<br />\n咁當然啦，我都係猜測冇證冇據，不過平時見到痴線西咁落力屌柒啲KOL無本生利賣返啲PR禮物出去，我就覺得打住為大家慳錢嘅旗號但係賣廠相送嘅禮物出去好可恥囉<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"blue\"><span class=\"violet\">冇咩經驗出po同做偵探，有冇痴線西有興趣接手？</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"8a8888852da7bbc1164184bd441f67eb747e39b0","tid":2425511,"uid":54486,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T11:29:42.000Z","msg":"有無文匯報賣？"},{"pid":"86076b748785a56cfe2f8fb0282f065a4eaadc26","tid":2425511,"uid":223376,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T11:30:42.000Z","msg":"召喚痴線西！"},{"pid":"56318958bcc573a263233c481e9c91b42ec918fb","tid":2425511,"uid":212623,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T11:30:50.000Z","msg":"嘩好撚肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好咁啦人哋要賺奶粉錢"},{"pid":"7688a7ddd86bdbeb56161b39a200dd0ceef5705e","tid":2425511,"uid":223376,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T11:31:10.000Z","msg":"召喚痴線西！"},{"pid":"e50226f620c953a5c233caa064855d45106feb30","tid":2425511,"uid":112316,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T11:32:17.000Z","msg":"地盤佬樣"},{"pid":"650033618af44d133960cac6123f5b5bd787f203","tid":2425511,"uid":64131,"like":2,"dislike":13,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T11:34:07.000Z","msg":"執埋執埋都係幾舊水都搞鳩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"149cef7152029009d2fd0acf9a9486e8e3237e04","tid":2425511,"uid":223376,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"56318958bcc573a263233c481e9c91b42ec918fb","tid":2425511,"uid":212623,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T11:30:50.000Z","msg":"嘩好撚肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好咁啦人哋要賺奶粉錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T11:34:45.000Z","msg":"有啲仲要擺到明係成set，但係佢哋要拆開幾支嚟賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2da9007f15a1ae91dcc8c9ddb3f47f737edcc35e","tid":2425511,"uid":128369,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T11:35:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b32a5b671b960e2527976a70f7b5e94cf43fd57","tid":2425511,"uid":212623,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2da9007f15a1ae91dcc8c9ddb3f47f737edcc35e","tid":2425511,"uid":128369,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"c